      "title": "Colombo - Man dies while waiting for fuel at Bampalapitiya",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo - A man died today (07) while waiting in line to get fuel at Pampalapitti filling station.",
        "The person who was waiting in the queue suddenly fell ill and was admitted to the Colombo National Hospital where he succumbed to his injuries."
